<br>
Clerics want fast slows so that they can use complete heals, warriors get pissed off when they lose agro to my slows.  Do you find it as frustrating as I do?  I'm just a bit upset right now I guess cause I've been told off by someone in my group for taking agro off the paladin <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqfaces.com/photos2/foursig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
