<br>
- Paladin or SK MA: Slow on sight if the mob can be slowed this way (PoV, BoT south wing). Malo then Slow if the mob has decent MR (BoT east for instance).<br>
<br>
- Warrior MA: A bit more tricky. If in a zone where Malo is requiered I Malo then Slow on sight, if warrior has decent weapons the 2 casting times plus recast let him take decent agro. If the mob can be slowed directly i either slow on sight and tank like 5 seconds (i can tank a slowed mob in PoV for a few seconds), or i wait till i see a proc message (&quot;Twists in Anger&quot;, or &quot;Contorts with rage&quot;) menaing the warrior has proced some huge agro from weapon. <p>Ginormus Sakapus - Burne n°6 - Oracle d'Aurore</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aaldaridrachenfuer>Aaldari Drachenfuer</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.enter.net/~betzenberger/Skeleton.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Egging EW</span><br>  Posts: 373<br> <font color=#628CBC>(4/16/03 9:26:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=68.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.enter.net/~betzenberger/aa.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: When do you slow?</span><hr size=1> Well luckily I group almost exclusivly with guildies and they rock, hands down.  I cannot get agro off our pallies if I try.<br>
<br>
That being said, I know the mobs we fight or learn really quickly.  If tash is not needed, I slow IMMEDIETLY.  Even if I get agro, it jumps back to MA pretty quickly.  If tash is needed, then I usually do both immedietly.  If group complains about me getting agro (non-guildies) I do one of two things.  If they are jerks, I wait a LONG time to slow and ask if this is how they want it done...only way I can do it with out agro.  If they are good people but maybe MA is a low warrior that needs a bit of help, I load up reacurring amnesia.  Hit tash, memblur, then slow.  That usualy does the trick.<br>
